trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> egenskap (och dess värde) för en utskrift maskinvaru- eller systemkomponent.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> klass för den angivna egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "DefaultPrintTicket", not "DefaultPrintSettings" or "Defaultprintticket".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objekt måste skrivas "DefaultPrintTicket", inte "DefaultPrintSettings" eller "Defaultprintticket".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> egenskap som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> klass som har det angivna värdet för den angivna egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "DefaultPrintTicket", not "DefaultPrintSettings" or "Defaultprintticket".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objekt måste skrivas "DefaultPrintTicket", inte "DefaultPrintSettings" eller "Defaultprintticket".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> egenskap som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Värdet på egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger värdet på egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintTicketProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that can be cast to a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som kan omvandlas till en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>
